    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes are starting to soften, add the <strong>roasted aubergine</strong> and <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat – this is your <strong>spicy aubergine sauce</strong></p><p>Once boiling, remove the pan from the heat and stir through your <strong>gnocchi</strong></p>",
