    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the contents of the pan<strong> </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Tear over the <strong>remaining 'Nduja </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), top with your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10-15 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>spicy 'Nduja & aubergine gnocchi bake</strong></p>",
