    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the gnocchi is baking, combine the<strong> remaining balsamic vinegar </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>to the<strong> </strong>balsamic dressing and gently mix together</p>",
